              >
              <p class="text-sm md:text-base font-bold text-white text-center">
                Remote cloud monitoring
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-span-1 lg:col-span-2 flex justify-end items-end">
          <img src={OSHand.src} alt="" class="w-3-4 lg:w-full" />
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full bg-bgBeige -skew-y-2">
      <div
        class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 py-20 max-w-7xl px-8 mx-auto skew-y-2 items-center"
      >
        <div class="w-full text-black">
          <h1 class="font-bold text-black text-xl md:text-2xl text-center">
            Triaso Asphalt Level Sensor
          </h1><br />
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg font-thin">
            Asphalt level sensor with guided wave radar technology, designed for
            continuous and accurate monitoring in real-time. <br />
            Asphalt volume in the tank (accuracy with a margin of error of 11.3 liters
            in 60,000 liters).
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 text-base md:text-lg font-thin">
            <li>Consumption and refill history of asphalt.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full text-center text-black flex justify-center">
          <img
            src={ASLevelSensor.src}
            alt=""
            class="w-full lg:w-3/4 rounded-xl"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl px-8 mx-auto py-20 flex flex-col gap-10">
      <h2 class="text-center text-2xl md:text-3xl">
        Simplifying Operations with Triaso Intelligent Features
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg font-thin">
        Beyond storage, our tanks are equipped with user-friendly features like
        automated monitoring systems, real-time data tracking, and efficient
        unloading mechanisms. These technologies help streamline operations,
        reduce maintenance, and enhance productivity across the board. With
        real-time access to trends, logs, and operational metrics,
        decision-making becomes faster, more informed, and fully independent of
        your physical location.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <ASCustom />
</section>
